      </div>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_382gc' title='Col. 382GC &mdash; HL Deb 14 September 2004 vol 664 c382GC' name='column_382gc' href='#column_382gc' rel='bookmark'>382GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-07657'>
